title: Hello, League Of Legends
body: My name is Ricky and I have had trouble logging into League of Legends. The thing is that when I click onto League Of legends application on my desktop it would show up a "LAUNCH" button, however on my screen it shows nothing. I don't know if other players have been experiencing this but I would like it to be resolves as soon as possible please because I do really enjoy this game, Thank You

replies.body: Have you tried running it in admin mode? Have you tried waiting for more than five minutes? It could just be patching the patcher itself, thus why it's not appearing.
